author: wn.com
title: Westboro Baptist Church to protest Kim Davis
text: The controversial Westboro Baptist Church, known for its anti-gay views, is planning on protesting "fake Christian" Kentucky county clerk Kim Davis, who grabbed the national spotlight in September when she refused to issue marriage licenses to same-sex couples, citing her religious views as the reason. ...
